    "image_with_text_kGt9y6": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_D9tiWj": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "✨ Low mess and low odor",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_KbCtpe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>These treats are dry and light. They won't make your hands sticky or oily or fill your pockets with crumbs. And you won't gag every time you use them.</p><h2>✨ Easily breaks to any size</h2><p>Our treats are already broken up into smaller pieces, and you can break them down more by snapping them with your fingers.</p><h2>✨ Pocket-friendly</h2><p>Our pocket tube is made for easy walks to the dog park, and a satisfying “pop” that will get your dog’s attention. And if you just need one treat, you can toss it in your pocket.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "caption_bY3d34": {
          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "📸 \"Doctor\" — Chihuahua + Mini Pin Mix, lives in New Mexico",
